ule running off track: Keep your plans flexible. A dash of skepticism could also be a benefit as people have their heads in the clouds and can be prone to fantasizing. If something doesn’t sound true, trust your instincts. Neptune ends its retrograde in Pisces on December 3, which can agai find people prone to fantasy. But meaningful discussions can take place, and it could also be a powerful moment to connect with your spirituality! <br><br>Venus squares off with Neptune on December 4, bringing a big dash of whimsy to your everyday routine! Romance gets a big boost, too. Keep your plans flexible as unexpected changes to your schedule could take place, or you may simply find yourself wanting more time to wander, explore, or rest. An overbooked schedule can find you stressed out<br>'),(33,'2023-01-02',4,'horoscope','Focusing on the larger picture now can help you be more resilient and at ease. This is a great time to look into getting a loan, whether it be for an investment or to pay off some debt. It\'s possible that you\'ll have to spend more on automobile or house repairs. Recognise the value of personal space in your relationships. Allow your partner to express their opinions freely. Contemplating marriage can evoke a range of feelings<br>'),(34,'2023-01-01',4,'horoscope','Kindred Spirits<br>Relationships are at the top of your agenda until January 20, Cancer, which is excellent for all kinds of romantic and business matters, collaborations, and other interactions. Over the coming weeks you’ll work better as part of a team than if you try to go solo. You’ll benefit from other people’s skills and expertise to get results that you could never manage alone.<br><br>The full moon in your sign on the sixth might need extra care, though, because you could feel vulnerable around this time. Emotions could come to the fore, and the slightest thing could leave you in tears. If you need to cry, just let it all out. You’ll feel much better.<br><br>In addition, feisty Mars turns direct in your sector of spirituality on January 12. This could inspire you to get in touch with a life coach or mentor who can help you overcome your limitations. You may have been especially aware of these when Mars was retrograde over recent weeks, but now is the time to do something about them.<br><br>Lovely Venus moves into your sector of finance and business on the second, followed by the radiant sun on the twentieth. The coming weeks are your opportunity to take your business to the next level while also digging deep to resolve any issues that are preventing your progress. On the one hand, you’ll be looking to make more money; on the other, you’ll want to streamline your affairs and get your money working harder for you.<br><br>The new moon in Aquarius on January 21 is the perfect time to kick-start new initiatives. Whether you want to start a business, launch a product, or make changes to the way you handle your finances, this is an excellent time to make your move.<br><br>Finally, lovely Venus moves into Pisces and your sector of new opportunities on the twenty-sixth. Your appetite for life could increase, and you’ll enjoy meeting people from other countries and cultures.<br>'),(35,'2023-01-01',4,'horoscope','Love will be at the forefront of your mind as the new year kicks off, dear Cancer, because four celestial bodies are moving through the sector of your chart that governs matters of the heart. Whether you’re single or in a relationship, you might want to consider setting resolutions around how to nurture healthy and supportive partnerships moving forward. However, these sentiments apply to all of your closest bonds, whether romantic or platonic.<br><br>You’ll feel a surge of cosmic energy surrounding you during the full moon in your sign on January 6. You can expect to feel more open-hearted and sensitive than usual, which can be a good or bad thing, depending on your situation. Take note of anyone or anything that drags your vibe down during this time, because it could be a nudge from the Universe that it’s time to move on to greener pastures. When all is said and done, this luminary event is all about prioritizing your needs.The vibe shifts when the sun enters Aquarius and the sector of your chart that governs transformation on the twentieth. If the full moon gave you insight on how your life needs to evolve, this solar placement provides you with the energy and motivation to make these changes happen. However, these vibes are fairly unpredictable, which means you might not always be in control of what stays in your orbit and what goes. But you should avoid spreading yourself too thin in order to fight for relationships or situations that leave you feeling drained.<br><br>Standout days: 12, 18, 21<br>Challenging days: 8, 16, 22<br>'),(36,'2023-01-01',4,'horoscope','In January, you should be very genuine with your own relationship. Positive planning and patience is likely to happen and also you should be careful in giving answers to others.<br><br>Mars can give good days after marriage. Some of you could get requests due to the Mars transit and this can lead to marriage or love relationships.<br><br>Health should be dealt with and some of you could get health related issues this month due to movement of planets. You could do well from your business and those of you who are proficient can likewise get financial benefit from your client.<br><br>Some of you could get postponement to get financial assistance from your family so you should be patient. Mars can offer you the chance to make things according to your plan at work.<br><br>You simply should stay away from forceful discussion with your team mate at the office. Rahu and Jupiter recommend you stay away from pressureful choice and furthermore don\'t get into workplace issues.<br><br>Venus transit can give good success at work with advancement and furthermore give the blessing of karma in return. Saturn can give results in a project related profession.<br><br