 month will be excellent for you when it comes to showing your talents. You are likely to get many opportunities.<br><br>Jupiter will bless you and hence you will be of benefit when it comes to completion of any projects. If you are in business, refrain from taking any major decisions.<br><br>Expect things to start rolling in your favour during the latter part of this month. This could be the best time for you to take advantage of learning opportunities that come your way.<br><br>Everything would seem to fall in right place due to blessings of Jupiter. There are possibilities of you getting into some minor tiffs with your schoolmates around the month end, indicates the Mars.<br><br>Try to keep your emotions and behavior under check. With the favorable aspect of Jupiter, you will benefit from a renewed vitality that takes you a step further in your efforts to raise the standard of your fitness levels during this month.<br>'),(91,'2023-02-01',10,'horoscope','In order to bring about change, it is important to take action and work towards your goals. This month, you may be focused on making progress towards your priorities and putting in extra effort to achieve your objectives. Your determination and hard work may be aligned, but it is also important to remember to respect the personal space of your partner and avoid any conflict. Spending quality time together can be enjoyable, but it is important to maintain a balance and allow for individual needs and boundaries.<br><br>Monthly Cosmic Tip: Take one project at a time. This will help you remain calm and more attentive to your priorities.<br>'),(92,'2023-02-01',10,'horoscope','They only think about one thing<br><br>If you get involved with a Capricorn, you live wildly and dangerously. Even outside the bedroom they are quickly excitable. At the slightest little thing you explode like a rocket! In a jubilant state or crossly unhappy - everything is possible in February. Everyone is at the feet of a Capricorn. However, not